title: French Hill (politician)
added: {{main|2020 United States House of Representatives elections in Arkansas#District 2}}

Hill ran for another term. [[Sarah Huckabee Sanders]] endorsed Hill, speaking at a rally in support of him.<ref>{{cite news |title=Sarah Huckabee Sanders encourages Arkansas voters at French Hill rally |url=https://www.thv11.com/article/news/politics/elections/sarah-huckabee-sanders-french-hill-rally/91-fe4d3618-0483-4bb6-befb-572fa2119273 |accessdate=20 November 2020 |work=THV 11 |date=31 October 2020}}</ref> In the November general election, Hill defeated Democratic nominee [[Joyce Elliot]].<ref>{{cite news |last1=Cushman |first1=Paige |title=French Hill wins re-election against Democratic opponent Joyce Elliott |url=https://katv.com/news/local/french-hill-wins-re-election-against-democratic-opponent-joyce-elliott |accessdate=20 November 2020 |work=KATV |date=3 November 2020}}</ref>
